### Update Category (full update)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics Updated",
  "slug": "electronics",
  "image-url": "https://example.com/images/electronics.jpg",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "display-order": 1
}

###

### Update Category - Change status to INACTIVE
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics",
  "slug": "electronics",
  "status": "INACTIVE",
  "display-order": 1
}

###

### Update Category - Change parent
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin/11
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Smartphones",
  "slug": "smartphones",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "display-order": 1,
  "parent-id": 2
}

###

### Update Category - Duplicate slug (expects error)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Electronics",
  "slug": "fashion",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "display-order": 1
}

###

### Update Category - Not Found
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/categories/admin/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ghost Category",
  "slug": "ghost-category",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "display-order": 1
}
